Privacy Policy for Ovum Hospitals App

Ovum Hospitals (“we”, “our”, or “us”) built the Ovum Hospitals app ("App") to provide patients and caregivers easy access to information, appointments, and hospital services. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information. By downloading or using our App, you agree to the practices described below.

1. Information We Collect
Personal Information
Provided directly by you: Name, email address, phone number, date of birth, gender, and payment details (only when booking services).
Automatically collected: Usage data (features accessed, time spent), device information (model, OS version), and crash reports.

Location Data
With your permission, we may collect approximate location to suggest nearby facilities and services.

2. How We Use Your Information
App functionality: To manage registrations, appointments, bookings, service reminders, and payments.
Communications: Send notifications for appointments, updates, and offers.
Improvement & analytics: Understand app usage, diagnose bugs, and enhance user experience.
Legal compliance: Fulfill regulatory, audit, or legal obligations.
3. Sharing & Disclosure
We do not share or sell your personal data with third parties outside our organization, except:
With service providers engaged to perform App-related functions (e.g., payment processors, analytics).
If required by law or to protect rights and safety.
4. User Choices
You can:
Update or delete account information via the App settings.
Enable or disable push notifications.
Manage or revoke location access permissions within your device’s settings.
5. Security Measures
We implement industry-standard safeguards (encryption, secure servers, limited access) to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or loss.
6. Children’s Privacy
The App is not intended for children under 16. We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors.
7. International Data Transfers
If you access the App outside India, be aware that your personal data may be processed on servers located in India in compliance with Indian data protection laws.
8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy. We will notify you via the App or email prior to changes taking effect. Continued use after notification means you accept the updated policy.
9. Contact Us
For any questions or concerns, please contact us at:
Website: https://www.ovumhospitals.com/
By using the Ovum Hospitals app, you confirm that you agree to this Privacy Policy.
